title: Almond Shortbread Recipe Demonstration - Joyofbaking.com
description:
Recipe here: http://www.joyofbaking.com/shortbreads/AlmondShortbreadCookies.html Stephanie Jaworski of Joyofbaking.com demonstrates how to make Almond Shortbread. These Almond Shortbreads are a nice cookie to have on hand. I often serve them in the afternoon with a hot cup of tea or for dessert, alongside a bowl of ice cream or a velvety smooth chocolate mousse. They have a sandy texture and subtle almond flavor which comes from adding ground almonds (almond flour or meal) to the batter. 

We welcome questions on our Facebook Page: http://www.facebook.com/joyofbaking
